name: Individual 500k HEN
description:
Live-rendered OBJKT to celebrate 500'000 OBJKTs on H=N, renders differently for every owner/viewer. All parameters are based on the unique seed of the owners' wallet-addresses.
First rendering is always based on the viewer-wallet-address, click/tap for next.

Click/Tap = Cycle owner variations
Space = Toggle Clearing
I = Invert Noise-Lines
M = Toggle Random or mouse-based Lines

Uses the hicdex API and therefore depends on it. This is all experimental and might break in the future. OBJKT uses p5js with p5.createloop and post5.
- @TeNinEightNFTs
